<item>
            <title>[PIG-3096] Make PigUnit thread safe</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3096</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, &lt;tt&gt;PigUnit&lt;/tt&gt; is not thread-safe because &lt;tt&gt;Cluster&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;PigServer&lt;/tt&gt; are declared as static. Converting them to ThreadLocal allows PigUnit to run in multi-threaded environment.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12624219">PIG-3096</key>
            <summary>Make PigUnit thread safe</summary>
